[recto] B.M. Wise & Foolish Virgins. Martin de Vos, Inventor, Crisp. de Passe impr.caelator. Set 1. frontispiece and five separate sheet. In Frontispiece: Vigilate quia nescitis diem neque horam qua filius hominis veniet, Matth. 25.cap. The same subjects as Bruegel [...]; [verso] [...] Ad [Addendum] Bruegel. The dancing group of the foolish virgins. The firts fully developed dance in Bruegel's oeuvre. There is nothing of its force yet in the background of Carnival & Lent in Vienne. Little Reigen.
